PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of JOHN UBERIG, of Nepean, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Petro-Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Donald D. Lusby, who has resigned.
